dataLineage.statement:
Layer was downloaded by ITOS from HDX. It was then analyzed by ITOS for errors. Those errors were corrected and then the layer was sent back to UNOCHA as a feature class within a file geodatabase.
The following was found and fixed by ITOS: 1. Created and populated reference name field 2. Populated Admin1 p-codes using values from https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ISO_3166-2:SA#Current_codes 3. Admin0 p-code has been converted from 3-letter ISO code to 2-letter code. 4. Found and fixed 2 small multipart slivers in unit "Makkah"
